{"tid":878162,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"開賣數日 上源已錄得10宗撻訂","createTime":"2018-10-27T02:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T08:42:24.000Z","uid":19552,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba59499a156e71338e60ab753da78ff3160d2fc","tid":878162,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"樓市淡風吹起，負面因素下，一手新盤買賣氣氛轉弱，地產站統計全港新盤成交紀錄冊，截至今日（10月24日），已錄得31伙撻訂單位，為近11個月新高，屯門上源佔10伙為最多。<br />\n<br />\n另外北角柏蔚山有建期買家放棄上會，該買家早於今年6月以2,236.3萬入市，購入2座6樓B室，面積823平方呎單位，並已簽署正式合約，但成交紀錄冊顯示已於本月22日終止買賣合約，提早離場。"},{"pid":"613cc3a22cbe344989b88dbce7c0d79d692138a2","tid":878162,"uid":6297,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"無實力買家，逃兵"},{"pid":"b4c7d209b3b30c474d538baaa502b86b3100908f","tid":878162,"uid":37733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"之前有連登囝用中獎黎形容中籤"},{"pid":"c1ee64f8846a9264e1fed472abbc86936e5a7a1c","tid":878162,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:10:07.000Z","msg":"唔敢成功"},{"pid":"fb3885b5440d432a38d21ca539de489c4ec093ba","tid":878162,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8n51EX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8n51EX.jpg&h=4154d9ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c91c207377a266f0c067f56cb42267eea3d091b","tid":878162,"uid":41963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:11:30.000Z","msg":"唔通樓主覺得會計?"},{"pid":"b76ae6d06878dc8f639de9bc9d9a56204685a8f3","tid":878162,"uid":158301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4c7d209b3b30c474d538baaa502b86b3100908f","tid":878162,"uid":37733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:09:26.000Z","msg":"之前有連登囝用中獎黎形容中籤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T02:11:45.000Z","msg":"依家係中槍"},{"pid":"38840c9ad2159b400270afef6a6c7f958ca75354","